# WhisperLiveKit Environment Configuration

# Hugging Face Token (required for some models)
# Get your token from: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
HF_TOKEN=hf_your_token_here

# Hugging Face Cache Directory (optional)
# Where to store downloaded HF models (also sets HF_HOME and HUGGINGFACE_HUB_CACHE)
HF_CACHE_DIR=/path/to/hf/cache

# Whisper Cache Directory (optional)
# Where to store downloaded Whisper models
# WHISPER_CACHE_DIR=/path/to/whisper/cache

# General Model Cache Directory (optional)
# Where to store other models
# MODEL_CACHE_DIR=/path/to/models/cache

# This token is required when using:
# - Speaker diarization (--diarization flag)
# - Punctuation restoration features

# Example usage:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Set your actual token and paths
# 3. Run: whisperlivekit-server --diarization

# Alternative: Login manually with:
# huggingface-cli login
